1. [Overview](#1-overview)
2. [Pipeline Steps at a Glance](#2-pipeline-steps-at-a-glance)
3. [Example 1 — NoBIAS + RMSX (Source 8 + 7)](#3-example-1--nobias--rmsx-source-8--7)
4. [Example 2 — Atlas + BGSU (Source 1 + 3)](#4-example-2--atlas--bgsu-source-1--3)
